            <title>小熊风冷降温电热水瓶预售：3.6L 容量、14 档保温可选，499 元</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/796/321.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/796/321.htm</guid>
